{
  "text": "The ratio of maximum variable fluorescence to maximum yield of fluorescence (Fv/Fm) that can be affected by the integrity of photosystem II (PSII) and used as an indicator for leaf senescence [CITATION_1] was measured using a PAM fluorometer (Walz GmbH, Effeltrich, Germany) [CITATION_2] .",
